{
  "video_id": "FcecqQkyKoM",
  "title": "Boghuma Kabisen Titanji: Ethical riddles in HIV research",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16837.0,
      "end_time": 18833.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18833.0,
      "end_time": 22669.0,
      "text": "the story of one of my patients called Celine."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22670.0,
      "end_time": 25823.0,
      "text": "Celine is a housewife and lives in a rural district"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25823.0,
      "end_time": 28895.0,
      "text": "of Cameroon in west Central Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28895.0,
      "end_time": 32582.0,
      "text": "Six years ago, at the time of her HIV diagnosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32582.0,
      "end_time": 35583.0,
      "text": "she was recruited to participate in the clinical trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35583.0,
      "end_time": 38654.0,
      "text": "which was running in her health district at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38654.0,
      "end_time": 42358.0,
      "text": "When I first met Celine, a little over a year ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42358.0,
      "end_time": 44410.0,
      "text": "she had gone for 18 months"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44420.0,
      "end_time": 46329.0,
      "text": "without any antiretroviral therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46329.0,
      "end_time": 49660.0,
      "text": "and she was very ill."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49660.0,
      "end_time": 51464.0,
      "text": "She told me that she stopped coming to the clinic"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51464.0,
      "end_time": 53150.0,
      "text": "when the trial ended"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53150.0,
      "end_time": 55726.0,
      "text": "because she had no money for the bus fare"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55726.0,
      "end_time": 59454.0,
      "text": "and was too ill to walk the 35-kilometer distance."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59454.0,
      "end_time": 61198.0,
      "text": "Now during the clinical trial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61198.0,
      "end_time": 65583.0,
      "text": "she&#39;d been given all her antiretroviral drugs free of charge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65583.0,
      "end_time": 67614.0,
      "text": "and her transportation costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67614.0,
      "end_time": 70221.0,
      "text": "had been covered by the research funds."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70221.0,
      "end_time": 73575.0,
      "text": "All of these ended once the trial was completed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73575.0,
      "end_time": 76567.0,
      "text": "leaving Celine with no alternatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76567.0,
      "end_time": 79243.0,
      "text": "She was unable to tell me the names of the drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79243.0,
      "end_time": 81270.0,
      "text": "she&#39;d received during the trial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81270.0,
      "end_time": 84270.0,
      "text": "or even what the trial had been about."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84270.0,
      "end_time": 87576.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t bother to ask her what the results of the trial were"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87576.0,
      "end_time": 91982.0,
      "text": "because it seemed obvious to me that she would have no clue."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91983.0,
      "end_time": 94252.0,
      "text": "Yet what puzzled me most"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94252.0,
      "end_time": 97359.0,
      "text": "was Celine had given her informed consent"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97359.0,
      "end_time": 101190.0,
      "text": "to be a part of this trial, yet she clearly did not understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101191.0,
      "end_time": 103661.0,
      "text": "the implications of being a participant"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 103661.0,
      "end_time": 108700.0,
      "text": "or what would happen to her once the trial had been completed."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108700.0,
      "end_time": 111464.0,
      "text": "Now, I have shared this story with you as an example"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111465.0,
      "end_time": 114394.0,
      "text": "of what can happen to participants in the clinical trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114394.0,
      "end_time": 116853.0,
      "text": "when it is poorly conducted."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116853.0,
      "end_time": 120717.0,
      "text": "Maybe this particular trial yielded exciting results."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120718.0,
      "end_time": 124407.0,
      "text": "Maybe it even got published in a high-profile scientific journal."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124407.0,
      "end_time": 127214.0,
      "text": "Maybe it would inform clinicians around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127214.0,
      "end_time": 132749.0,
      "text": "on how to improve on the clinical management of HIV patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132749.0,
      "end_time": 135535.0,
      "text": "But it would have done so at a price"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135535.0,
      "end_time": 138482.0,
      "text": "to hundreds of patients who, like Celine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138482.0,
      "end_time": 140726.0,
      "text": "were left to their own devices"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140726.0,
      "end_time": 143797.0,
      "text": "once the research had been completed."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 143797.0,
      "end_time": 147135.0,
      "text": "I do not stand here today to suggest in any way"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147135.0,
      "end_time": 149148.0,
      "text": "that conducting HIV clinical trials"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149148.0,
      "end_time": 151363.0,
      "text": "in developing countries is bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151363.0,
      "end_time": 155730.0,
      "text": "On the contrary, clinical trials are extremely useful tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155730.0,
      "end_time": 158280.0,
      "text": "and are much needed to address the burden"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158280.0,
      "end_time": 160499.0,
      "text": "of disease in developing countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160499.0,
      "end_time": 163358.0,
      "text": "However, the inequalities that exist between"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163358.0,
      "end_time": 167600.0,
      "text": "richer countries and developing countries in terms of funding"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167600.0,
      "end_time": 170217.0,
      "text": "pose a real risk for exploitation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170217.0,
      "end_time": 174102.0,
      "text": "especially in the context of externally-funded research."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174102.0,
      "end_time": 176708.0,
      "text": "Sadly enough, the fact remains that"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176708.0,
      "end_time": 180692.0,
      "text": "a lot of the studies that are conducted in developing countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 180692.0,
      "end_time": 183268.0,
      "text": "could never be authorized in the richer countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183268.0,
      "end_time": 185516.0,
      "text": "which fund the research."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 185516.0,
      "end_time": 187762.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure you must be asking yourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 187763.0,
      "end_time": 189679.0,
      "text": "what makes developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 189679.0,
      "end_time": 192223.0,
      "text": "especially those in sub-Saharan Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 192223.0,
      "end_time": 195790.0,
      "text": "so attractive for these HIV clinical trials?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195790.0,
      "end_time": 199610.0,
      "text": "Well, in order for a clinical trial to generate"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199620.0,
      "end_time": 202178.0,
      "text": "valid and widely applicable results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 202178.0,
      "end_time": 206178.0,
      "text": "they need to be conducted with large numbers of study participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 206178.0,
      "end_time": 208821.0,
      "text": "and preferably on a population"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 208821.0,
      "end_time": 212602.0,
      "text": "with a high incidence of new HIV infections."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 212602.0,
      "end_time": 216730.0,
      "text": "Sub-Saharan Africa largely fits this description,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 216730.0,
      "end_time": 219275.0,
      "text": "with 22 million people living with HIV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 219275.0,
      "end_time": 222915.0,
      "text": "an estimated 70 percent of the 30 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 222915.0,
      "end_time": 225396.0,
      "text": "who are infected worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 225396.0,
      "end_time": 227826.0,
      "text": "Also, research within the continent"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 227826.0,
      "end_time": 231938.0,
      "text": "is a lot easier to conduct due to widespread poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 231938.0,
      "end_time": 235789.0,
      "text": "endemic diseases and inadequate health care systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 235789.0,
      "end_time": 238577.0,
      "text": "A clinical trial that is considered to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 238578.0,
      "end_time": 241328.0,
      "text": "potentially beneficial to the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 241328.0,
      "end_time": 243635.0,
      "text": "is more likely to be authorized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 243635.0,
      "end_time": 246435.0,
      "text": "and in the absence of good health care systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 246435.0,
      "end_time": 249389.0,
      "text": "almost any offer of medical assistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 249389.0,
      "end_time": 252307.0,
      "text": "is accepted as better than nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 252307.0,
      "end_time": 254893.0,
      "text": "Even more problematic reasons include"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254893.0,
      "end_time": 257180.0,
      "text": "lower risk of litigation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 257180.0,
      "end_time": 259647.0,
      "text": "less rigorous ethical reviews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 259647.0,
      "end_time": 262203.0,
      "text": "and populations that are willing to participate"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 262203.0,
      "end_time": 266866.0,
      "text": "in almost any study that hints at a cure."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 266867.0,
      "end_time": 270492.0,
      "text": "As funding for HIV research"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 270492.0,
      "end_time": 272748.0,
      "text": "increases in developing countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 272748.0,
      "end_time": 276755.0,
      "text": "and ethical review in richer countries become more strict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 276755.0,
      "end_time": 278840.0,
      "text": "you can see why this context becomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 278840.0,
      "end_time": 281400.0,
      "text": "very, very attractive."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 281401.0,
      "end_time": 285810.0,
      "text": "The high prevalence of HIV drives researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 285810.0,
      "end_time": 289565.0,
      "text": "to conduct research that is sometimes scientifically acceptable"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289565.0,
      "end_time": 292844.0,
      "text": "but on many levels ethically questionable."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 292844.0,
      "end_time": 296283.0,
      "text": "How then can we ensure that, in our search for the cure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 296283.0,
      "end_time": 298603.0,
      "text": "we do not take an unfair advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 298603.0,
      "end_time": 302107.0,
      "text": "of those who are already most affected by the pandemic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 302107.0,
      "end_time": 305963.0,
      "text": "I invite you to consider four areas I think we can focus on"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 305963.0,
      "end_time": 309538.0,
      "text": "in order to improve the way in which things are done."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 309538.0,
      "end_time": 312365.0,
      "text": "The first of these is informed consent."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 312365.0,
      "end_time": 314733.0,
      "text": "Now, in order for a clinical trial to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 314733.0,
      "end_time": 318414.0,
      "text": "considered ethically acceptable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 318414.0,
      "end_time": 321238.0,
      "text": "participants must be given the relevant information"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 321238.0,
      "end_time": 323673.0,
      "text": "in a way in which they can understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 323673.0,
      "end_time": 327890.0,
      "text": "and must freely consent to participate in the trial."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 327890.0,
      "end_time": 330568.0,
      "text": "This is especially important in developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 330568.0,
      "end_time": 333469.0,
      "text": "where a lot of participants consent to research"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 333470.0,
      "end_time": 336158.0,
      "text": "because they believe it is the only way in which"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 336158.0,
      "end_time": 339728.0,
      "text": "they can receive medical care or other benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 339728.0,
      "end_time": 342695.0,
      "text": "Consent procedures that are used in richer countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 342695.0,
      "end_time": 345497.0,
      "text": "are often inappropriate or ineffective"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 345497.0,
      "end_time": 347850.0,
      "text": "in a lot of developing countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 347850.0,
      "end_time": 350823.0,
      "text": "For example, it is counterintuitive to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 350823.0,
      "end_time": 353822.0,
      "text": "an illiterate study participant, like Celine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 353822.0,
      "end_time": 357149.0,
      "text": "sign a lengthy consent form that they are unable to read,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 357149.0,
      "end_time": 359256.0,
      "text": "let alone understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 359256.0,
      "end_time": 362335.0,
      "text": "Local communities need to be more involved"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 362336.0,
      "end_time": 365609.0,
      "text": "in establishing the criteria for recruiting participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 365609.0,
      "end_time": 370310.0,
      "text": "in clinical trials, as well as the incentives for participation."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 370310.0,
      "end_time": 372126.0,
      "text": "The information in these trials"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 372126.0,
      "end_time": 375770.0,
      "text": "needs to be given to the potential participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 375770.0,
      "end_time": 379505.0,
      "text": "in linguistically and culturally acceptable formats."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 379505.0,
      "end_time": 382326.0,
      "text": "The second point I would like for you to consider"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 382326.0,
      "end_time": 384764.0,
      "text": "is the standard of care that is provided"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 384764.0,
      "end_time": 387710.0,
      "text": "to participants within any clinical trial."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 387710.0,
      "end_time": 391407.0,
      "text": "Now, this is subject to a lot of debate and controversy."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 391407.0,
      "end_time": 394388.0,
      "text": "Should the control group in the clinical trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 394388.0,
      "end_time": 397661.0,
      "text": "be given the best current treatment which is available"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 397661.0,
      "end_time": 399741.0,
      "text": "anywhere in the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 399741.0,
      "end_time": 402709.0,
      "text": "Or should they be given an alternative standard of care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 402709.0,
      "end_time": 405597.0,
      "text": "such as the best current treatment available"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 405597.0,
      "end_time": 408909.0,
      "text": "in the country in which the research is being conducted?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 408909.0,
      "end_time": 412248.0,
      "text": "Is it fair to evaluate a treatment regimen"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 412249.0,
      "end_time": 415325.0,
      "text": "which may not be affordable or accessible"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 415325.0,
      "end_time": 419295.0,
      "text": "to the study participants once the research has been completed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 419295.0,
      "end_time": 423360.0,
      "text": "Now, in a situation where the best current treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 423360.0,
      "end_time": 425675.0,
      "text": "is inexpensive and simple to deliver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 425675.0,
      "end_time": 427703.0,
      "text": "the answer is straightforward."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 427703.0,
      "end_time": 430852.0,
      "text": "However, the best current treatment available"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 430853.0,
      "end_time": 433740.0,
      "text": "anywhere in the world is often very difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 433740.0,
      "end_time": 436427.0,
      "text": "to provide in developing countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 436427.0,
      "end_time": 439979.0,
      "text": "It is important to assess the potential risks and benefits"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 439979.0,
      "end_time": 442756.0,
      "text": "of the standard of care which is to be provided"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 442756.0,
      "end_time": 445236.0,
      "text": "to participants in any clinical trial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 445237.0,
      "end_time": 450685.0,
      "text": "and establish one which is relevant for the context of the study"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 450685.0,
      "end_time": 454182.0,
      "text": "and most beneficial for the participants within the study."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 454182.0,
      "end_time": 457433.0,
      "text": "That brings us to the third point I want you think about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 457433.0,
      "end_time": 460284.0,
      "text": "the ethical review of research."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 460284.0,
      "end_time": 464820.0,
      "text": "An effective system for reviewing the ethical suitability"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 464830.0,
      "end_time": 468211.0,
      "text": "of clinical trials is primordial to safeguard participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 468211.0,
      "end_time": 470324.0,
      "text": "within any clinical trial."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 470324.0,
      "end_time": 473236.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, this is often lacking"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 473236.0,
      "end_time": 476764.0,
      "text": "or inefficient in a lot of developing countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 476764.0,
      "end_time": 481127.0,
      "text": "Local governments need to set up effective systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 481127.0,
      "end_time": 484400.0,
      "text": "for reviewing the ethical issues around the clinical trials"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 484400.0,
      "end_time": 487921.0,
      "text": "which are authorized in different developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 487921.0,
      "end_time": 490195.0,
      "text": "and they need to do this by setting up"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 490195.0,
      "end_time": 492705.0,
      "text": "ethical review committees that are independent"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 492705.0,
      "end_time": 496900.0,
      "text": "of the government and research sponsors."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 496900.0,
      "end_time": 498500.0,
      "text": "Public accountability needs to be promoted"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 498500.0,
      "end_time": 501733.0,
      "text": "through transparency and independent review"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 501733.0,
      "end_time": 504772.0,
      "text": "by nongovernmental and international organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 504772.0,
      "end_time": 506343.0,
      "text": "as appropriate."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 506343.0,
      "end_time": 509853.0,
      "text": "The final point I would like for you to consider tonight"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 509853.0,
      "end_time": 513760.0,
      "text": "is what happens to participants in the clinical trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 513760.0,
      "end_time": 515851.0,
      "text": "once the research has been completed."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 515851.0,
      "end_time": 519325.0,
      "text": "I think it is absolutely wrong for research to begin"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 519325.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521837.00000000006,
      "text": "in the first place without a clear plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 521837.0,
      "end_time": 523915.0,
      "text": "for what would happen to the participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 523916.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526356.0,
      "text": "once the trial has ended."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 526356.0,
      "end_time": 531484.0,
      "text": "Now, researchers need to make every effort to ensure that"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 531484.0,
      "end_time": 534468.0,
      "text": "an intervention that has been shown to be beneficial"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 534468.0,
      "end_time": 536199.0,
      "text": "during a clinical trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 536200.0,
      "end_time": 539812.0,
      "text": "is accessible to the participants of the trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 539812.0,
      "end_time": 542360.0,
      "text": "once the trial has been completed."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 542360.0,
      "end_time": 545884.0,
      "text": "In addition, they should be able to consider the possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 545884.0,
      "end_time": 549485.0,
      "text": "of introducing and maintaining effective treatments"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 549485.0,
      "end_time": 553326.0,
      "text": "in the wider community once the trial ends."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 553326.0,
      "end_time": 556749.0,
      "text": "If, for any reason, they feel that this might not be possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 556749.0,
      "end_time": 559716.0,
      "text": "then I think they should have to ethically justify"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 559716.0,
      "end_time": 563743.0,
      "text": "why the clinical trial should be conducted in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 563743.0,
      "end_time": 566590.0,
      "text": "Now, fortunately for Celine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 566590.0,
      "end_time": 568733.0,
      "text": "our meeting did not end in my office."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 568734.0,
      "end_time": 573108.0,
      "text": "I was able to get her enrolled into a free HIV treatment program"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 573108.0,
      "end_time": 574496.0,
      "text": "closer to her home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 574496.0,
      "end_time": 578270.0,
      "text": "and with a support group to help her cope."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 578270.0,
      "end_time": 580603.0,
      "text": "Her story has a positive ending,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 580604.0,
      "end_time": 584307.0,
      "text": "but there are thousands of others in similar situations"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 584307.0,
      "end_time": 586604.0,
      "text": "who are much less fortunate."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 586604.0,
      "end_time": 589280.0,
      "text": "Although she may not know this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 589280.0,
      "end_time": 592893.0,
      "text": "my encounter with Celine has completely changed the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 592893.0,
      "end_time": 597164.0,
      "text": "in which I view HIV clinical trials in developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 597164.0,
      "end_time": 600884.0,
      "text": "and made me even more determined to be part of the movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 600884.0,
      "end_time": 603741.0,
      "text": "to change the way in which things are done."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 603741.0,
      "end_time": 606109.0,
      "text": "I believe that every single person"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 606109.0,
      "end_time": 610484.0,
      "text": "listening to me tonight can be part of that change."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 610484.0,
      "end_time": 613810.0,
      "text": "If you are a researcher, I hold you"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 613810.0,
      "end_time": 615651.0,
      "text": "to a higher standard of moral conscience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 615651.0,
      "end_time": 618780.0,
      "text": "to remain ethical in your research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 618780.0,
      "end_time": 621566.0,
      "text": "and not compromise human welfare in your search for answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 621566.0,
      "end_time": 625244.0,
      "text": "If you work for a funding agency or pharmaceutical company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 625244.0,
      "end_time": 628274.0,
      "text": "I challenge you to hold your employers"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 628274.0,
      "end_time": 631449.0,
      "text": "to fund research that is ethically sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 631449.0,
      "end_time": 634635.0,
      "text": "If you come from a developing country like myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 634635.0,
      "end_time": 637707.0,
      "text": "I urge you to hold your government"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 637707.0,
      "end_time": 640323.0,
      "text": "to a more thorough review of the clinical trials"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 640323.0,
      "end_time": 643236.0,
      "text": "which are authorized in your country."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 643236.0,
      "end_time": 646904.0,
      "text": "Yes, there is a need for us to find a cure for HIV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 646904.0,
      "end_time": 649556.0,
      "text": "to find an effective vaccine for malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 649556.0,
      "end_time": 653398.0,
      "text": "to find a diagnostic tool that works for T.B.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 653398.0,
      "end_time": 656973.0,
      "text": "but I believe that we owe it to those who willingly"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 656973.0,
      "end_time": 661270.0,
      "text": "and selflessly consent to participate in these clinical trials"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 661280.0,
      "end_time": 663254.0,
      "text": "to do this in a humane way."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 663254.0,
      "end_time": 665581.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ]
}